          2.2.7 Read MUD Instruction                ____________________

          Syntax:  REAd Mud

          Description:  The read  MUD instruction allows the user  to read any
               block of a  MUD.   The  operator  must  input  the block number
               and the sup number.  VAL will build  a circuit through the net-
               work if necessary  and retrieve the information  desired by the
               operator.

