          VAL Users Guide                                   September 26, 1980



          CUD OVERFLOW!

               There is no room for more CUD entries.

          ERROR DETECTED IN BLOCK NUMBER 1329

               The CUD block has a checksum error.

          EXPECTED BLOCK 1234 RECEIVED BLOCK 1235

               A CUD block is missing from the CUD tape.

          FAILED TRANSFERRING BLOCK - CHECKSUMS DO NOT MATCH

               A CUD block could not be transferred to the other supervisor.

          ILLEGAL CHARACTER ENTERED, TRY AGAIN

               A semicolon, escape, or carriage return was included in a pass-
